<plot>Sprawl is a prose recounting that contemplates and examines our relationship with a living planet. The moving images are documents to the splendors of life and our sometimes careless interaction with the other living things. Through familiar imagery it reveals our humble and proud natures as it also uncovers the silent casualties of suburban sprawl and over- development</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?511484</url></doc>
